These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, magic-tricks
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, water-polo
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, taxi
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks    | singing |
| Sport         | water-polo | skiing    |
| Transport     | roller     | taxi      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, lacrosse
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, turkish
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, train
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the canadian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Sport      | lacrosse  | surfing   |
| Nationality   | turkish | canadian  |
| Transport     | train   | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, writing
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, martial-arts
2 different pets are kept: bird, fish
1. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | collecting   | writing  |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | fantasy  |
| Pet         | bird   | fish |

 #################################

 
